 &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://222.180.160.110:61235/contest/4434&#34;&gt;NOIP S&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&#34;https://vjudge.net/contest/594162&#34;&gt;计数杂题&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;
